============================================================================

  Introduction.
  -------------

  You are now about to start the building of this Oscilloscope. Make sure
  that you understand the ~?.drawing~ files and the following text before
  continuing because any error can be catastrophic to the A1200 on power up.
  I have been as thorough as possible with the ~?.drawing~ files and I am
  sure that there are no errors. However you may find one before you power
  your unit up. If you do find an error let me know as soon as possible on
  my Email address at the end of this text file.

                                IMPORTANT:-
                                -----------


